verbose_text: AR and 3beta-HSD were not expressed in first trimester testes at 9 weeks of gestation, but were expressed in the same testes 6 weeks after xenografting, indicating that steroidogenesis is beginning to occur and that the testes are becoming androgen responsive : SMA expression in peritubular myoid cells is considered to be androgen dependent.
